Lara Belmont https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lara_Belmont 0 Lara Belmont (born 1980 in Oxford, Oxfordshire) is an English actress, most famous for her role as Jessie in the 1999 film The War Zone. She also appeared in ITV's lavish costume drama Henry VIII as his eldest daughter Mary Tudor. Belmont worked as a model before she was spotted in the street by a casting director.
